<br>
    1) pets are almost always 90 - 100% health ( barring resisted darkness/fears )<br>
     2) Total mana cost over time reduced greatly by using the dots of the necro combined with 2 pets and one Char from me. <br>
     3) Malo line of spell to pull as necro is casting darkness almost always ensures that their darkness sticks and seems to keep them from getting over aggro ( which a necro can easily with the darkness line ) <br>
